{"tid":2222452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳同佳打手們，跟陳同佳有親？","createTime":"2020-09-29T05:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T06:17:01.000Z","uid":377390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"197f26c5832fb4cd574374e6ea6a0880764e9cdb","tid":2222452,"uid":377390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"可能有人同陳同佳有親，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想係連登帶風向。<br />\n<br />\n以自由與人性之名營造一個陳同佳逃避殺人責任是理所當然的局面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話女方不忠在先，<br />\n但她既不忠罪名係用係性命償還代價。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男方殺人衣食無憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要我地班納稅人日日返工做到狗冇啖好食供養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初陳同佳出來面對公眾講到好想返去台灣受審咁，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲諗住有下文，點知就龜縮無了期。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又話呢壇野要逃犯條例先搞得店，實質就借力賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n好彩香港人頂得住先唔洗硬食。<br />\n<br />\n追根究底引發一連串事件既當時人只係需要負上洗黑錢罪名，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就話一齊推佢返台灣受審，買定花生睇報應，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張機票就可以一大巴咁車落去呢個賣港政權到，<br />\n證明到要立逃犯條例係無風起浪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申我同呢單野既人或事無任何關係，只係我睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32c38e6e1cb084802bb4381cc812b5c06aba4bb","tid":2222452,"uid":19640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"197f26c5832fb4cd574374e6ea6a0880764e9cdb","tid":2222452,"uid":377390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"可能有人同陳同佳有親，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想係連登帶風向。<br />\n<br />\n以自由與人性之名營造一個陳同佳逃避殺人責任是理所當然的局面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.g